Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道自己在幹什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫慰的帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特隊隊長亞伯力克·基烈特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來報道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於嘉依卡 我隊除當初追捕的一名外又增加一名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下正追蹤兩名嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他隊有什麼新情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前沒什麼實質上的進展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關長 我想再看一下賈茲皇帝的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些及其他從賈茲城收押的東西都保管在書庫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 事到如今還有什麼好查的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞伯力克 這五年來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對嘉依卡的案件一直很重視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但關於皇帝的詳細情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話即便如今我們已經擊殺了他 仍然對他不夠了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡收集遺體的行為真會對我們造成威脅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個嘉依卡從我眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走了阿巴爾特伯爵擁有的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的目的與「威脅」相差甚遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 祭悼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括有裝鎧龍與他們一同行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有些地方令人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我實在看不出他們有顛覆國家的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是有些別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞伯力克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從嘉依卡的案件抽手一段時間怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡的問題確實是很重要的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但目前 我們的首要職責
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是實際改善大陸人民的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須以這為最優先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振動大 操縱 難關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們特地選了條小路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這根本稱不上是路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個將你和機車連接起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並通過魔法思念料驅動它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與機杖 同樣構造
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化石 礦石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體中所含生物的記憶 思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部 魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的思念料 一切魔法之源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈茲皇帝的遺體也是很強大的魔法思念料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長 你知道現今大部分魔法技術是誰發明的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是賈茲皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這機車和機杖 都是你爸發明的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 偉大的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交通行費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是新賈茲帝國的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0110,0040,,{\fs38}NeoGaz
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得賈茲帝國 自從五年前皇帝被殺就滅亡了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是渴望復興帝國之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現正與去世皇帝的遺孤 嘉依卡公主一同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此地建立新的帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚愕的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是將軍馬拉德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及大臣拉布魯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是近衛隊隊長弗洛魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那位就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新賈茲帝國的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 嘉依卡喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無禮 要向嘉依卡公主多表敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且把通行費交了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行許可 申請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟拿銀幣出來 你腦子裡在想些什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看你們很是可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我們還得趕路…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要檢查一下車內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是道具箱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是這城來那鎮去的候鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在這個村子 明天在那個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家帶去幸福的江湖賣藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江湖賣藝人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 也為了證明你們的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來給嘉依卡公主表演些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我很想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新賈茲城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不准何時又會有六國聯盟的追兵前來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此這只是為瞞過世人眼睛的暫時的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以這裡的皇帝之女嘉依卡公主為旗首
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以新賈茲帝國的復活為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫離開國家的賈茲帝國國民們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬眾一心集結在了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者還另有對六國聯盟心懷不滿的有志之士們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在支持我們的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國復興之日已近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天讓大家欣賞幾項我們的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於本事還未到家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有失誤 還請多多包涵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出的這個蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神奇 扔出去也不會落地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 怎麼樣 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這邊的蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神奇 它會把飛向少女的匕首都吸過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像在哪兒見過?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這隻小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是隻只要施展咒語 就會顯露出本性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乎其神的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏拉 烏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏拉 烏拉 烏拉 烏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏拉拉 烏拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了 那女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全神貫注中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…這事不要太鑽牛角尖比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人在等我?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於賈茲皇帝有弄明白什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說沒什麼有價值的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連他出生相關的情報都不明不白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為至少應該會有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝到死前一直著手的最前沿技術的資料的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼關於嘉依卡的事情呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽說有殘黨想擁立嘉依卡企圖復興帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有實際確認到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人 今天的用餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我今天從早上到現在還什麼都沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起去吃個飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好棒的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街頭藝人體力很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在棺材裡放隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果一打開變成了裝鎧龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個戲法 到底是怎麼辦到的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微透露一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛魯 你喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡所有人 賈茲帝國國民?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你們也是賈茲帝國出身?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼不早說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我馬上拿去換成軍資金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了喔 同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了賈茲帝國的復興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重振皇室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新賈茲帝國萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗屁新賈茲帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了不就是一群盜賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已經吃足一枚銀幣的飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要繼續待下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 名字叫做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡和托魯是什麼關係?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的表演 兩人配合好默契啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是兄妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡他?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定 堅決否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新賈茲帝國 復興 希望?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想給因戰爭而流離失所的賈茲帝國國民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供一處棲身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 我想重建帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有棲身之所 幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的 大家的幸福?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 芙蕾多妮卡也是賈茲人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能不能一起來幫忙復興帝國?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起去拜訪資產家的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請他們給予資金援助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要芙蕾多妮卡開口請求他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家都會慷慨解囊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫幫我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法忘懷的 有你的冬天的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等候 你那身影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比凍結的吐息更清白的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比大地更清澈的藍色眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞麻色的頭髮如琥珀般閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情詩?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這是賈茲帝國的詩人的詩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想記下來嗎 我教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 你那如陽光般的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將顫抖的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主 請移駕執務室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天再繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 約定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩兒是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再加把勁就能攻陷她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外兩人交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把錢全弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那機車也一定不能放過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人有約不能走?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續和那幫傢伙糾纏可沒好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點趕路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯正確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我 約定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那約定有這麼重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會被那套新賈茲帝國建國的說辭騙到了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是收集父親遺體吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定 接著反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚出發 明早出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差別無大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路況很差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明早再走較為明智
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且沒嘉依卡開車 機車也動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再出發也無妨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性 道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是心太軟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉布魯負責食堂的銀餐具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿貯藏庫裡的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量挑些值錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陷阱 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是舊賈茲帝國的國民吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有意與我們一起復興賈茲帝國嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做江湖藝人 四處漂泊也很辛苦吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據你們的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證給你們相應的地位喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉失敗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是普通的江湖藝人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過通緝令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡帶著棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一頭銀色頭髮 有一對紫色眼瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:15:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要借嘉依卡這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起碼先調查清楚再借啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早說啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是曾經想說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們剛才胡扯什麼復興賈茲帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是想也捲走我們的錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計你的同伴也都是這樣騙入夥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本沒想騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我們是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 目標太過遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是維持每日的生計就已經精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是被生活所迫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們也沒有完全放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日會將帝國…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬拉德 出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉婭她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們穿幫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉婭怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那是個陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們徹底中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我問你尤莉婭去哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的牢房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到沒 明白了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不願再添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯還是挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 尤莉婭 救出 請求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫再牽扯較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉婭 約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢房在地下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能帶人從那裡逃出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不可能的 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法使用 救出可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 努力 尤莉婭 救出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:17:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧 沉默不語者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Silencer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正被六國聯盟追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已才藏身此處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你出去 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 你們不是來救我了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我們道聲謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 要謝就謝嘉依卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝搭救之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地包裹著顫抖的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以春天的光輝填滿我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈茲的冬景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的你就是春天的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永不忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起 我欺騙了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡為什麼旅行?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 祭悼 為了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你目標早日實現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝福 感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是時候做個轉變了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的路又該怎麼走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 再尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物歸原主我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能問件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈茲皇帝是什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如人品之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算問我 我連他長什麼樣都沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽大家都說是個了不得的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們住在鄉下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不清楚皇帝的事情 日子也是照樣過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連那個他為了研發魔法技術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行了非常可疑的人體實驗的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是戰後才聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 實際情況我們一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還問這個做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是隨便問問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們今後打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直拖延下來的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候付諸行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連賈茲帝國的國民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不清楚皇帝的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸真是充滿謎團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 他們今後打算怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再發現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 再發現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是很嚴重的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派往加瓦爾尼公爵領
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求返還航天要塞索厄拉的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟被殺害 變成淒慘的屍體回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須立即進行武力制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法思念料 枯竭在即
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採購 必須
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今天 終戰紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店舖皆休息 我為難
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周 第九集 「記憶的價值」
