Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.71,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}って思う　って思う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:48.63,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}愛の馬鹿　視界不良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:52.81,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}どうしろって言うんだ　この夜に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:56.81,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行き止まり　で指切り
